<figureCitation box="[269,349,513,539]" captionStart="FIGURES 10–15" captionStartId="4.[151,264,748,773]" captionTargetBox="[157,1429,174,724]" captionTargetId="figure@4.[151,1436,166,729]" captionTargetPageId="4" captionText="FIGURES 10–15. Subgen. Merocratus (aedeagi, schematically, not in scale). 10—Anthaxia (M.) jakli Bílý, 1996, holotype; 11—A. (M.) miranda Deyrolle, 1864 (Kalimantan); 12—A. (M.) angustata sp. nov., Bílý, holotype; 13—A. (M.) priska Bílý, sp. nov., holotype; 14—A. (M.) violaceidorsis Bílý, sp. nov., holotype; 15—A. (M.) lucifera Plachetka, sp. nov., holotype." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3557863" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/3557863/files/figure.png" pageId="6">Fig. 13</figureCitation>
